3. cs.DS - The paper discusses the search algorithms used in CDCL solvers, which is a topic in data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.PL - The paper discusses the implementation of heuristics in an ASP solver, which is a topic in programming languages. 
5. cs.SE - The paper discusses the performance of CDCL solvers on real-world problems, which is a topic in software engineering.
